author: ebu
msg: Refactored overriding of Array.prototype to ExtArray functions.
This overriding prevented 3rd party scripts from using arrays as maps.

author: arj
msg: Complete, radical overhaul of the standard CSS jspwiki.css. It is organized (!) and significantly trimmed back from its former sprawling self. Note the new <div> classes "error" "information" and "warning". These have been substituted into one-timer classes like "versionnote". The styles, overall, have had most of the rough edges rubbed out... not perfect but it's a start -- not all of Dirk's recommendations made it in.

author: arj
msg: Added attribute "div" to <wiki:Messages> tag to allow messages to be neatly wrapped. Default class is "information". This required minor tweaks to several JSPs.
